output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes, contains "CMF11240017" which indicates this is electoral propaganda 2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions "Marcel Ciolacu" and promotes him for presidential elections 3. Addresses wide population: Yes, it's a paid Facebook post targeting a large audience (100,001-500,000 people) 4. Electoral objective: Yes, explicitly calls for votes for PSD and Marcel Ciolacu in both parliamentary and presidential elections 5. Journalism: No, this is clearly campaign material, not journalistic content 6. Personal opinion: While it contains personal experiences, it's structured as campaign material with clear call to action for voting
The post violates Article 55 t) as it: - Continues electoral propaganda for presidential elections after the conclusion of the campaign period - Contains explicit call to vote for a presidential candidate (Marcel Ciolacu) - Is a paid advertisement reaching a large audience - Uses official campaign materials (CMF number)

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Contains official campaign identifier (CMF) - Directly promotes a presidential candidate - Contains explicit call to vote - Is a paid advertisement - Uses party symbols and messaging - Links personal story to party promotion
conclusion.message-for-police: Infomed Pro SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale după încheierea campaniei electorale prezidențiale, prin publicarea și sponsorizarea unui mesaj pe Facebook (ID post: 1109886473308382) care îndeamnă explicit la votarea candidatului ION-MARCEL CIOLACU la alegerile prezidențiale. Postarea, activă după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, conține număr CMF (CMF11240017), utilizează mesaje de campanie și îndeamnă direct la vot pentru un candidat prezidențial specific, încălcând astfel perioada de blackout electoral. Mesajul a fost distribuit către un public țintă estimat între 100,001 și 500,000 de persoane, amplificând astfel impactul încălcării.
